<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no" />
        <meta name="description" content="" />
        <meta name="author" content="" />
        <title>주차관리 시스템</title>
        <!-- Favicon-->
        <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="assets/favicon.ico" />
        <!-- Core theme CSS (includes Bootstrap)-->
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" type="text/css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/intro.css" type="text/css">
        <!-- Load C3 -->
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/c3/0.4.11/c3.min.css"/>
        <script src="https://d3js.org/d3.v3.min.js"></script>
        <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/c3/0.4.11/c3.min.js"></script>

        <link rel="stylesheet" href="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/morris.js/0.5.1/morris.css">
        <script src="//ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.min.js"></script>
        <script src="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/raphael/2.1.0/raphael-min.js"></script>
        <script src="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/morris.js/0.5.1/morris.min.js"></script>

    </head>
    <body>
        <!-- Responsive navbar-->
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
            <div class="container">
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">Linked Park</a>
            </div>
        </nav>
        <!-- Page content-->
        <div class="container">
            <div class="text-center mt-5">
                <h1>주차 점유 현황</h1>
                <p class="lead">최근 6개월 간의 주차 데이터를 바탕으로 한 주차 점유율을 확인해보세요.</p>
                <br/><br/>

                <h4>전체 점유 현황</h4>
                <div id="monthlyAll" style="height: 250px;"></div>
                <script>
                    const totalData = <%- JSON.stringify(totalData) %>;
                    new Morris.Bar({
                        element: 'monthlyAll',
                        data: totalData,
                        xkey: 'time',
                        ykeys: ['value'],
                        ymax: 100,
                        postUnits: '%',
                        labels: ['Value'],
                        barColors: ['green'],
                    });
                </script>
                <br/><br/>
                
                <h4>거주자 점유 현황</h4>
                <div id="monthlyResident" style="height: 250px;"></div>
                <script>
                    const residentData = <%- JSON.stringify(residentData) %>;
                    new Morris.Bar({
                        element: 'monthlyResident',
                        data: residentData,
                        xkey: 'time',
                        ykeys: ['value'],
                        ymax: 100,
                        postUnits: '%',
                        labels: ['Value'],
                        barColors: ['#1531B2'],
                    });
                </script>
                <br/><br/>
                
                <h4>방문자 점유 현황</h4>
                <div id="monthlyVistor" style="height: 250px;"></div>
                <script>
                    const visitorData = <%- JSON.stringify(visitorData) %>;
                    new Morris.Bar({
                        element: 'monthlyVistor',
                        data: visitorData,
                        xkey: 'time',
                        ykeys: ['value'],
                        ymax: 100,
                        postUnits: '%',
                        labels: ['Value'],
                        barColors: ['#b21532'], 
                    });
                </script>
                <br/> 
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Bootstrap core JS-->
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
        
    </body>
</html>